msgstr "Hibernate Reactive Panache 使用 `io.quarkus.hibernate.reactive.panache.PanacheEntity` 代替 `io.quarkus.hibernate.orm.panache.PanacheEntity` 。有关详细信息，请参阅 link:{quickstarts-tree-url}/security-jpa-reactive-quickstart/src/main/java/org/acme/elytron/security/jpa/reactive/User.java[用户文件] 。"

